name: NYI RORO KIDUL
description: Hello everyone, this is my genesis at Hicetnunc. Titled Nyi Roro Kidul is a legendary Indonesian spirit or goddess who is very popular among the people of Java and Bali. This figure is known as the Queen of the South Sea (Indian Ocean) and is generally equated with Kanjeng Ratu Kidul, although according to some circles the two are actually different.
